column5:
A good western\, but not perfect. The game has:- nice\, photorealistic graphics;- beautiful physics.;
- excellent approach to details and trifles (the corpse of the killed animal rots\, the character removes the weapon from the safety\, traces on snow do not disappear for a long time);
- great atmosphere and spirit of the time;
